      h4 Train stations
      p The closest train stations to Dangeau are in Bonneval (10 mins) and Chateaudun (20 mins). Trains leave every couple hours from Paris Gare d'Austerlitz. They take approximately 1.5 hours and cost ~25 Euros. Rental cars are available in Chateaudun, but not in Bonneval.
